OL,3,CArson murder accused 'wanted to
OL,4,Cinflict maximum pain'
OL,6,FA man accused of murdering a mother
OL,7,Fand her three children in a house fire
OL,8,F"wanted to inflict maximum pain" and
OL,9,F"didn't care who was there", a trial
OL,10,Fhas heard.
OL,12,FProsecutors say Sharaz Ali was
OL,13,F"motivated by jealousy and fuelled by
OL,14,Fdrink and drugs" when he set fire to
OL,15,Fthe home of Bryonie Gawith and her
OL,16,Fchildren in the early hours of 21
OL,17,FAugust last year.
