OL,3,CArson murder accused 'wanted to
OL,4,Cinflict maximum pain'
OL,6,FAli, 40, is accused of starting the
OL,7,Ffire as "revenge" on his former
OL,8,Fpartner ` Bryonie's sister Antonia
OL,9,FGawith ` who was staying at the
OL,10,FBradford property after ending their
OL,11,F"abusive" seven-year relationship.
OL,13,FGiving his closing speech at Doncaster
OL,14,FCrown Court on Friday, prosecutor
OL,15,FDavid Brooke KC said the case had been
OL,16,F"particularly grim".
