OL,3,CArson murder accused 'wanted to
OL,4,Cinflict maximum pain'
OL,6,FHe told jurors: "Whilst a trial can
OL,7,Fsometimes show us the best of humanity
OL,8,F` think of the actions of those first
OL,9,Ftwo police officers who went into that
OL,10,Fburning house ` equally it can expose
OL,11,Fus to the worst of human behaviour.
OL,13,F"Little did those officers know they
OL,14,Fwere saving a man who had, moments
OL,15,Fbefore, deliberately set fire to a
OL,16,Fhouse with a mother and her children
OL,17,Fupstairs, knowing he was condemning
OL,18,Fthem to, at the very least, really
OL,19,Fserious harm, if not death.
OL,26,@nD@QOUuD@AOU
