OL,3,CArson murder accused 'wanted to
OL,4,Cinflict maximum pain'
OL,6,F"And why? A deep and persistent anger
OL,7,Fand jealousy towards his former
OL,8,Fpartner Antonia, fuelled by drink and
OL,9,Fdrugs ` an action designed to inflict
OL,10,Fmaximum pain on her, both physically,
OL,11,Fas he soaked her in petrol, and
OL,12,Fmentally, as he took his revenge on
OL,13,Fher and her sister."
OL,15,FThe court has heard Ali went into the
OL,16,Fhouse in Westbury Road and started
OL,17,Fpouring petrol around inside, as well
OL,18,Fas on himself and Antonia Gawith.
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@TO]
