OL,3,CArson murder accused 'wanted to
OL,4,Cinflict maximum pain'
OL,6,FShe fled, but Ali used a lighter to
OL,7,Fstart a "catastrophic" blaze which
OL,8,Fkilled Bryonie and her three children,
OL,9,FDenisty Birtle, nine, Oscar Birtle,
OL,10,Ffive, and 22-month-old Aubree Birtle.
OL,12,FAli told the trial that he wanted to
OL,13,Fkill himself in front of Antonia, and
OL,14,Fonly intended to set himself alight.
OL,16,FAli was rescued from the fire by
OL,17,Fpolice who had arrived at the scene
OL,18,Ffirst.
OL,26,@oD@IOUoD@VO]
