OL,3,CArson murder accused 'wanted to
OL,4,Cinflict maximum pain'
OL,6,FMr Brooke said in the days before the
OL,7,Ffire Ali had sent messages to Antonia
OL,8,FGawith saying: "I know who caused this
OL,9,Fin my life and deep down you do too."
OL,11,FThe prosecutor said: "When it comes to
OL,12,Fmotivation, you don't just have
OL,13,FAntonia's evidence, you have those
OL,14,Ftexts, setting out clear as could be
OL,15,Fthe anger, the resentment, the self-
OL,16,Fpity, the drunkenness, the threats."
OL,26,@pD@POUsD@VOUxD@dO]
