OL,3,CArson murder accused 'wanted to
OL,4,Cinflict maximum pain'
OL,6,FMr Brooke told the court that Ali
OL,7,F"must have known" the children were at
OL,8,Fhome, saying: "He didn't care who was
OL,9,Fthere ` he wanted to inflict maximum
OL,10,Fdamage on anyone he could find in that
OL,11,Fhouse."
OL,13,FHe said Antonia Gawith had told police
OL,14,Fthat Ali "loved the kids ... as part
OL,15,Fof her incomprehension at how he could
OL,16,Fhave done this to them".
OL,18,FHe told jurors: "We know from the
OL,19,Ftexts that it didn't stop him
OL,20,Fthreatening her sister and the
OL,21,Fchildren."
