OL,6,FMr Brooke said the relationship
OL,7,Fbetween Ali and Antonia Gawith had
OL,8,Fbeen abusive and that it was Bryonie,
OL,9,Fwho "had gone through her own
OL,10,Fstruggles" and was separated from her
OL,11,Fpartner, who persuaded her sister to
OL,12,Fleave.
OL,14,FAli, of no fixed address, and Calum
OL,15,FSunderland, 26, of Calton Street,
OL,16,FKeighley, are charged with murdering
OL,17,FBryonie Gawith and the three children,
OL,18,Fand attempting to murder Antonia
OL,19,FGawith.
OL,26,@qD@EOUrD@JO]
