OL,6,FMohammed Shabir, 45, who had been due
OL,7,Fto go on trial with them, died of a
OL,8,Fheart attack last month after
OL,9,Fcollapsing in prison.
OL,11,FProsecutors say Shabir drove to and
OL,12,Ffrom the house while Sunderland kicked
OL,13,Fthe door in.
OL,15,FSunderland told the trial he had been
OL,16,Fenlisted by Ali to "torch a car" and
OL,17,Fdid not know there were people in the
OL,18,Fhouse.
OL,20,FAli and Sunderland deny the charges
OL,21,Fand the trial continues.
